/**
 * @fileoverview
 *   Collapse white-space.
 *
 *   Normally, collapses to a single space.
 *   If `newlines: true`, collapses white-space containing newlines to `'\n'`
 *   instead of `' '`.
 * @example
 *   <h1>Heading</h1>
 *   <p><strong>This</strong> and <em>that</em></p>
